# WKBackgroundFetchResult.newData

**Case**

The download attempt succeeded.

## Declaration

```swift
case newData
```

## Fetch Results

- **WKBackgroundFetchResult.failed**: The download attempt failed.
- **WKBackgroundFetchResult.noData**: The notification has no associated content.
